description.zh: 与《疯狂动物城》的朱迪和尼克在繁华的动物都市自拍，画面充满活力与欢乐，仿佛置身于动画世界。
description.en: A vibrant selfie with Judy Hopps and Nick Wilde in the bustling city of Zootopia, capturing the joy and energy of the animated world.

items.title: 女生双手比出一个心形

description.zh: 一位女生用双手比出心形手势，背景柔和，传递出温暖与爱意。
description.en: A girl forms a heart shape with her hands against a soft background, conveying warmth and affection.

description.zh: 一张复古宝丽来照片，定格了温馨的日常瞬间，褪色的色彩与边框仿佛在轻声诉说着一段私人的故事。
description.en: A vintage Polaroid photo captures a warm, everyday moment, with faded colors and a frame that quietly whispers a personal story.

description.zh: 宝丽来照片的复古色调与独特质感，将瞬间定格为充满故事感的视觉叙事，唤起温暖回忆。
description.en: The retro tones and unique texture of Polaroid photos freeze moments into visual narratives full of storytelling, evoking warm memories.

description.zh: 九张女性肖像照以3x3网格排列，展现多样表情与光影，形成富有张力的视觉拼贴。
description.en: A 3x3 grid collage of female portraits, capturing diverse expressions and lighting to create a compelling visual narrative.

items.title: 四幅女子时尚生活场景拼贴画

description.zh: 四幅拼贴画展现都市女性的多元时尚生活，从咖啡馆阅读到街头漫步，呈现优雅与活力的视觉叙事。
description.en: A four-panel collage depicting urban women's fashionable lifestyles, from café reading to street strolls, showcasing elegant and dynamic visual storytelling.

items.title: 模切线图转3D产品可视化

description.zh: 将平面模切线图转化为生动的3D产品可视化，精准呈现结构细节与立体质感，助力设计沟通与决策。
description.en: Transforming 2D die-cut line drawings into vivid 3D product visualizations, accurately showcasing structural details and texture to enhance design communication and decision-making.

description.zh: 模切线从平面设计稿中跃然而出，化为真实立体的三维形态，展现从概念到现实的创意转化过程。
description.en: Die-cut lines leap from the flat design, transforming into tangible 3D forms that visualize the creative journey from concept to reality.

items.title: 城市俯视等距3D卡通微缩场景

description.zh: 俯瞰视角下的等距3D卡通城市微缩场景，充满活力与细节，仿佛一个精致的立体模型世界。
description.en: An isometric 3D cartoon miniature city scene from a bird's-eye view, bursting with vibrant life and intricate details like a charming diorama.

description.zh: 将真人照片转化为3D漫画风格，保留人物特征的同时增添动漫质感，实现从现实到虚拟的趣味转变。
description.en: Transform real-life photos into 3D cartoon style, retaining personal features while adding anime texture for a fun shift from reality to virtuality.

items.title: 虚构的英语电影海报-回忆之味

description.zh: 一幅虚构的英语电影海报，以复古色调和模糊的餐桌场景，唤起关于家庭与逝去时光的深刻情感与味觉记忆。
description.en: A fictional English movie poster in vintage tones, featuring a blurred dining scene that evokes deep emotions and taste memories of family and bygone times.

description.zh: 卡哇伊波普艺术融合了可爱元素与大胆色彩，以扁平化设计呈现充满活力的流行文化场景，风格鲜明有趣。
description.en: Kawaii Pop Art blends cute elements with bold colors, presenting vibrant pop culture scenes in a flat design style that is distinctive and playful.

description.zh: 金属质感与霓虹光影交织的创意手账，充满未来科技感与个性表达。
description.en: A creative notebook blending metallic textures with neon glow, exuding futuristic tech vibes and personal expression.

description.zh: iPhone 16 Pro Max 内部结构深度解析，高清拆解图清晰展示精密元器件布局与创新设计细节。
description.en: An in-depth look inside the iPhone 16 Pro Max, with high-resolution teardown images revealing the intricate layout of components and innovative design details.

description.zh: 清新蓝色手账，点缀简约手绘与文字，营造出宁静而富有创意的个人记录空间。
description.en: A fresh blue notebook with minimalist hand-drawn elements and text, creating a serene and creative space for personal reflection.

description.zh: 精密相机内部结构拆解图，齿轮、镜片与机械组件在白色背景上精确排列，展现工业美学与科技细节。
description.en: Exploded view of camera mechanism with precisely arranged gears, lenses and components on white background, revealing industrial aesthetics and technological details.

description.zh: 复古动漫风格下的奇幻世界，柔和色调与怀旧笔触交织，营造出既梦幻又充满故事感的视觉氛围。

items.title: 东方武侠史诗海报-剑影红颜

description.en: An epic wuxia poster where sword gleams meet a beauty's grace, blending ink-wash artistry with martial valor and tender passion.

items.title: 奇幻冒险喜剧海报-寻龙秘境

description.en: Fantasy adventure comedy poster 'Dragon's Hidden Realm', depicting protagonists stumbling into a mysterious dragon territory, embarking on a treasure hunt filled with unexpected dangers and hilarious mishaps.

items.title: 鱼眼镜头下的日本女子比心

description.en: A Japanese girl playfully makes a heart gesture under a fisheye lens, creating an exaggerated visual tension full of youthful energy.

items.title: 年轻女子侧坐在街机凳上

description.zh: 一位年轻女子侧坐在复古街机凳上，霓虹灯光映照着她的侧影，营造出怀旧又充满活力的氛围。

description.zh: 油泼面宫格漫画图，以九宫格形式生动展现油泼面制作过程，画面充满动感与食欲，风格鲜明有趣。

description.zh: 皮克斯风格3D动画场景，充满温暖光影与生动角色，营造出梦幻般的童话世界，细节丰富情感饱满。

description.en: A Pixar-style 3D animation scene with bright, warm colors, featuring adorable rounded characters, brimming with childlike wonder and imagination, as if stepping into a dreamy animated world.

items.title: 掌上游戏机的精美3D渲染图

description.en: An exquisite 3D render of a retro handheld console, featuring rich details, realistic textures, and nostalgic tech aesthetics.

items.title: 身着白色针织上衣的阳光女孩

description.zh: 一位身着白色针织上衣的女孩，在阳光下展露温暖笑容，画面柔和明亮，充满青春气息。
description.en: A girl in a white knit top smiles warmly in the sunlight, creating a soft and bright scene filled with youthful energy.

items.title: 早朝了开个视频会议先

description.en: An emperor in dragon robe opens a laptop on his throne, holding a remote video morning court with officials, a humorous blend of ancient and modern.

items.title: 游戏角色试图从电视屏幕爬到客厅

description.zh: 游戏角色正从电视屏幕中奋力爬出，试图进入客厅，画面充满奇幻与紧张感。
description.en: A video game character struggles to climb out of the TV screen into the living room, creating a surreal and tense scene.

description.zh: 泛黄旧报纸手账，复古质感与手写文字交织，承载时光记忆的创意拼贴艺术。
description.en: A vintage newspaper journal with yellowed pages, blending retro texture and handwritten notes into a creative collage of timeless memories.

description.zh: 一只可爱的金毛犬坐在电脑前，戴着耳机，仿佛正在认真地进行网络直播，画面温馨又有趣。
description.en: An adorable Golden Retriever sits in front of a computer wearing headphones, as if seriously hosting a live stream, creating a warm and amusing scene.

description.zh: 一个外星人站在飞碟旁，友好地向地球挥手，背景是璀璨的星空和蓝色星球，充满科幻与好奇的氛围。
description.en: An alien stands beside a flying saucer, waving friendly towards Earth against a backdrop of a starry sky and the blue planet, evoking a sense of sci-fi wonder and curiosity.

items.title: 李小龙与尤达大师以武会友

description.zh: 李小龙与尤达大师在竹林中对决，东西方武学智慧碰撞，光影交错间展现力量与哲思的融合。
description.en: Bruce Lee duels Master Yoda in a bamboo forest, where Eastern and Western martial arts wisdom collide, blending power and philosophy in dynamic light.

description.zh: 明星们在闪光灯后放松的瞬间，捕捉到镜头外的真实互动与欢笑，展现聚光灯下的另一面。
description.en: A candid behind-the-scenes moment captures stars relaxing and sharing genuine laughter away from the flashbulbs, revealing the unscripted side of fame.

items.title: 马里奥路易吉给碧奇公主修理厨房

items.title: 西游记师徒四人组成了一个摇滚乐队

description.en: The Journey to the West quartet transforms into a rock band, with Wukong on vocals, Bajie on bass, Sha Seng on drums, and Tang Seng on keyboards, performing passionately on the Flaming Mountain stage.

description.en: A humorous 'National First-Class Slacking License' image in a vintage document style, featuring a lazy panda or reclining cartoon character, humorously certifying a state-approved leisurely attitude.

items.title: 未经他人苦莫劝他人善

description.en: A weary worker sits in a dimly lit stairwell, where interplay of light and shadow conveys the weight and solitude of life, echoing the profound sentiment: 'Do not judge until you have walked in their shoes.'

description.en: Sitting alone by the window late at night, moonlight pours like water, accompanied by coffee and books, a quiet yet awake romantic moment.

items.title: 宇航员坐在弯弯的月亮边钓星星

description.zh: 宇航员悠闲地坐在弯月边缘，手持钓竿垂向星空，仿佛在垂钓闪烁的星辰，画面充满童话般的想象力与宁静感。
description.en: An astronaut sits casually on the crescent moon's edge, fishing rod in hand, casting a line toward the starry sky as if angling for twinkling stars, creating a whimsical and serene scene.

description.zh: 一张创意职业生涯地图，以手绘路线图形式展现职业发展路径，包含关键节点与未来目标，风格清新且富有启发性。

description.zh: 一张充满趣味的人物特写，捕捉到人们做出夸张Emoji表情的瞬间，展现生动情绪与创意互动。
description.en: A fun close-up portrait capturing people making exaggerated emoji expressions, showcasing vivid emotions and creative interaction.

description.zh: 长平之战信息图，以简洁的视觉元素呈现战役关键数据、双方布阵与历史影响，一目了然。
description.en: An infographic of the Battle of Changping, visually presenting key data, troop deployments, and historical impact with clear graphics.

description.zh: 识字小报元提示词：用AI生成趣味识字海报，将汉字与生动图像结合，激发儿童学习兴趣。
description.en: Literacy Poster Meta Prompts: Use AI to create engaging literacy posters that combine Chinese characters with vivid imagery, sparking children's learning interest.

description.zh: 一幅充满张力的大幅油画肖像，笔触粗犷有力，色彩浓郁饱满，生动捕捉人物深邃情感与独特气质。
description.en: A large-scale oil portrait with bold, expressive brushstrokes and rich colors, vividly capturing the subject's deep emotion and unique character.

items.title: 我的世界神秘时代信息卡

description.zh: 一张《我的世界》神秘时代模组的信息卡，展示着魔法符文与古代知识，在像素方块世界中散发着神秘光芒。
description.en: A Mystcraft information card from Minecraft, glowing with magical runes and ancient knowledge within its pixelated block world.

description.zh: 一幅融合传统水墨与现代设计的流年运势图，以抽象线条与星象符号交织，展现时光流转与命运起伏的深邃意境。
description.en: A fusion of traditional ink wash and modern design, this fortune chart intertwines abstract lines with astrological symbols, capturing the profound flow of time and destiny.

items.title: Labubu和迪丽热巴高端时尚跨页大片

description.zh: Labubu与迪丽热巴惊艳同框，演绎时尚与潮玩的跨界碰撞，高级质感大片展现独特艺术张力。
description.en: Labubu and Dilraba stun together in a high-fashion editorial, blending urban vinyl art with celebrity glamour in a visually striking crossover.

description.zh: 风格化的3D人物漫画，以夸张的卡通造型和鲜艳色彩呈现，充满活力与幽默感，适合游戏角色或动画设计。
description.en: A stylized 3D character comic with exaggerated cartoon forms and vibrant colors, full of energy and humor, ideal for game characters or animation design.

items.title: 一张年轻女性的逼真特写自拍照

description.zh: 一张年轻女性的逼真特写自拍照，眼神清澈柔和，自然光线下肌肤纹理细腻，展现真实而动人的瞬间。
description.en: A realistic close-up selfie of a young woman, with clear gentle eyes and delicate skin texture under natural light, capturing an authentic and touching moment.

description.zh: 通过拆解衣橱单品，分析个人风格与穿搭逻辑，构建更高效、更具表达力的日常着装体系。
description.en: Deconstruct your wardrobe to analyze personal style and outfit logic, building a more efficient and expressive daily dressing system.

items.title: 绘制地标的手绘等距示意图

description.zh: 手绘等距示意图，以独特视角展现地标建筑的立体结构，线条生动且充满设计感。
description.en: A hand-drawn isometric diagram showcasing the three-dimensional structure of a landmark with dynamic lines and artistic flair.

description.zh: 一张充满动感的《龙珠》主题卡牌，角色能量爆发，卡面设计华丽，极具收藏价值。

description.zh: 专业摄影棚内，模特身着简约时装，在柔和光线与纯色背景前展现优雅姿态，呈现高端商业质感。

description.zh: 极简构图下，一杯清澈鸡尾酒置于纯白背景，冰块折射光线，营造出宁静而高级的视觉氛围。
description.en: A clear cocktail on a pure white background, with ice cubes refracting light, creating a serene and sophisticated minimalist composition.

description.zh: 将经典动漫角色通过AI技术转化为逼真的真人形象，展现独特的视觉魅力与艺术再创造。

description.en: A premium poster for Dan Dan Noodles, featuring glossy chili oil and crushed peanuts in moody lighting, paired with minimalist calligraphy, elevating street food to gourmet art.

description.zh: 通过精准的提示词复刻经典图像风格，展现AI绘画对细节与氛围的还原能力，实现创意再现。
description.en: Recreate iconic image styles with precise prompts, showcasing AI's ability to restore details and atmosphere for creative reproduction.

description.zh: 达芬奇名画《最后的晚餐》的现代AI重绘，融合赛博朋克光影与未来主义细节，呈现科技与信仰的碰撞。
description.en: A cyberpunk reinterpretation of Da Vinci's 'The Last Supper', blending neon-lit futurism with classical composition in an AI-generated vision.

items.title: 宫崎骏的角色走进最后的晚餐

description.zh: 宫崎骏动画中的经典角色齐聚一堂，以《最后的晚餐》构图呈现，奇幻与古典艺术交织出宁静而神秘的氛围。
description.en: Hayao Miyazaki's iconic characters gather in a serene, mystical reinterpretation of 'The Last Supper', blending fantasy with classical artistry.

description.zh: 通过构建视觉化的记忆宫殿，将英语单词与生动场景关联，让学习过程如探索奇幻世界般高效有趣。
description.en: Associate English vocabulary with vivid scenes by constructing a visual memory palace, making learning as efficient and engaging as exploring a fantasy world.
